# QA artifacts — regenerated per `npm run test:browser` / `npm run test:qa`.
# ALL report artifacts are now untracked: they're produced fresh on every
# launcher run (test:grids / test:browser / test:qa / test:fs each writes
# its own latest.md). Tracking them caused FAST_PATH to NEVER activate
# (git status always dirty) → Boki saw "stuck for 3-5 min" every double
# click instead of the intended sub-10s warm boot.
reports/

# tools/diff-pdf-vs-md intermediate dumps + headless test screenshots
tools/_diff-*
tools/_eyes/

# Wave UQ — Ultimate QA staged HTML artifacts (regenerated each run).
# Synthetic fixtures + manifest ARE tracked (source-of-truth for matrix).
tools/_qa/ultimate-html/

# Launcher fast-path cache — local-only, regen-uje se na svaki run.
.last-build-hash

# Claude Code local state
.claude/
*.bak
.tmp-308/

# Wave Z.2 — per-block live demo HTMLs (generated by tools/gen-block-demos.mjs)
blocks/demos/
reports/playwright-deep-qa/
reports/screen-reader-walk/
reports/bundle-size/
reports/i18n-locale-sweep/
reports/cross-browser/
